King (company) - Wikipedia






















 






King (company)

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


King Digital Entertainment plc





Type

Subsidiary


Industry
Video game industry


Founded
August 2003; 13 years ago (2003-08)


