Who are the Candy Crush millionaires?









King Digital Entertainment's stock flotation is set to give its biggest shareholders multi-million dollar windfalls















































King's Thomas Hartwig and Sebastian Knutsson. Photograph: /PR










IPOs




Who are the Candy Crush millionaires?









King Digital Entertainment's stock flotation is set to give its biggest shareholders multi-million dollar windfalls












